data.description: LOOK! Mount Pleasant 3 bedroom Duplex - 2 large bedrooms upstairs both have walk in closets , large bedroom on the main with a full bathroom. Lots of storage.  Large kitchen opens to the dining and includes two pantry's. Nice screened porch & utility storage overlooking private backyard space. Easy access to everything including Lowe's grocery Harris Teeter, gas and restaurants, minutes to Costco. The Dunes West community offers wonderful amenities to include 3 pools, clubhouse, fitness gym, tennis courts & golf membership is available. Close to beach and shopping.
